#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn1.31"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn1.31:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 1 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 1 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn1.31:0.2"
msgid "4. Satullapakāyikavagga "
msgstr "4. The Satullapa Group "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn1.31:0.3"
msgid "31. Sabbhisutta "
msgstr "31. Virtuous "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: pts1ed1.17, sc1
msgctxt "sn1.31:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "sn1.31:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn1.31:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho sambahulā satullapakāyikā devatāyo abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. "
msgstr "Then, late at night, several glorious deities of the Satullapa Group, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side, "

msgctxt "sn1.31:1.4"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho ekā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "and recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn1.31:2.1"
msgid "“Sabbhireva samāsetha, "
msgstr "“Associate only with the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: kubbetha → krubbetha (bj, mr)
msgctxt "sn1.31:2.2"
msgid "sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
msgstr "Try to get close to the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:2.3"
msgid "Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding the true teaching of the good, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:2.4"
msgid "seyyo hoti na pāpiyo”ti. "
msgstr "things get better, not worse.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn1.31:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then another deity recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.38, sc4
msgctxt "sn1.31:4.1"
msgid "“Sabbhireva samāsetha, "
msgstr "“Associate only with the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:4.2"
msgid "sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
msgstr "Try to get close to the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:4.3"
msgid "Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding the true teaching of the good, "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: paññā labbhati → paññaṃ labhati (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn1.31:4.4"
msgid "paññā labbhati nāññato”ti. "
msgstr "wisdom is gained—but not from anyone else.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn1.31:5.1"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then another deity recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn1.31:6.1"
msgid "“Sabbhireva samāsetha, "
msgstr "“Associate only with the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:6.2"
msgid "sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
msgstr "Try to get close to the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:6.3"
msgid "Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding the true teaching of the good, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:6.4"
msgid "sokamajjhe na socatī”ti. "
msgstr "you don’t sorrow even among those who sorrow.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn1.31:7.1"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then another deity recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "sn1.31:8.1"
msgid "“Sabbhireva samāsetha, "
msgstr "“Associate only with the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:8.2"
msgid "sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
msgstr "Try to get close to the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:8.3"
msgid "Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding the true teaching of the good, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:8.4"
msgid "ñātimajjhe virocatī”ti. "
msgstr "you shine among your relatives.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "sn1.31:9.1"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then another deity recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.39, sc10
msgctxt "sn1.31:10.1"
msgid "“Sabbhireva samāsetha, "
msgstr "“Associate only with the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:10.2"
msgid "sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
msgstr "Try to get close to the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:10.3"
msgid "Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding the true teaching of the good, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:10.4"
msgid "sattā gacchanti suggatin”ti. "
msgstr "sentient beings go to a good place.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "sn1.31:11.1"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then another deity recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "sn1.31:12.1"
msgid "“Sabbhireva samāsetha, "
msgstr "“Associate only with the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:12.2"
msgid "sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
msgstr "Try to get close to the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:12.3"
msgid "Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding the true teaching of the good, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:12.4"
msgid "sattā tiṭṭhanti sātatan”ti. "
msgstr "sentient beings live happily.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc13
msgctxt "sn1.31:13.1"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then another deity said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn1.31:13.2"
msgid "“kassa nu kho, bhagavā, subhāsitan”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, who has spoken well?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc14
msgctxt "sn1.31:14.1"
msgid "“Sabbāsaṃ vo subhāsitaṃ pariyāyena, api ca mamapi suṇātha—"
msgstr "“You’ve all spoken well in your own way. However, listen to me also: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.18, sc15
msgctxt "sn1.31:15.1"
msgid "Sabbhireva samāsetha, "
msgstr "Associate only with the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:15.2"
msgid "sabbhi kubbetha santhavaṃ; "
msgstr "Try to get close to the virtuous! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:15.3"
msgid "Sataṃ saddhammamaññāya, "
msgstr "Understanding the true teaching of the good, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.31:15.4"
msgid "sabbadukkhā pamuccatī”ti. "
msgstr "you’re released from all suffering.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc16
msgctxt "sn1.31:16.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "sn1.31:16.2"
msgid "Attamanā tā devatāyo bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyiṃsūti. "
msgstr "Then those deities, knowing that the teacher approved, bowed and respectfully circled the Buddha, keeping him on their right, before vanishing right there."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
